This paper is about data center networking (DCN), which is a subfield of computer networking. The paper specifically focuses on hybrid circuit and packet switching, which is a topic related to network architecture and design. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Other likely sub-categories include cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.PF (Performance).
